headline.main: Poland Lacks Backing in Quest to Unseat EU's Tusk
headline.print_headline: Poland Lacks Backing in Quest to Unseat EU's Tusk

lead_paragraph: A push by Poland's eurosceptic government to remove fellow-countryman Donald Tusk from one of the top jobs in the European Union failed to win any public support on Monday as EU foreign ministers met to discuss it in Brussels.
